skill.desc: Fire a chain that deals magic damage and Stuns for 1 seconds. The chain links to the 3 closest enemies, dealing magic damage to each.

skill.name: Bat Bolts
skill.desc: Rapidly fire 3 attacks. The first two deal bonus true damage, and the final attack deals bonus true damage.

skill.name: Cyber Supremacy
skill.desc:
Deal magic damage to the current target.

If Veigar is the same star level as the target, deal 25% true damage. If Veigar is a higher star level, deal 40% true damage.

skill.name: Retribution
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 18% Omnivamp. 150% of overhealing from Retribution's damage is converted to bonus true damage to its primary target.

Active: Send a shadow to the target, dealing magic damage to all enemies it passes through. The shadow then explodes, dealing magic damage to the target and to enemies within 1 hex.

skill.name: Block Chain
skill.desc: Gain Shield that rapidly decays over 4 seconds. Vi's next attack deals physical damage.

skill.name: Holoblade
skill.desc:
Passive: When units die, absorb their soul and heal Health.

Active: Jump to the largest clump of enemies within 2 hexes, dealing magic damage to adjacent enemies and magic damage to other enemies within 2 hexes. 20% Shred all enemies hit for 4 seconds.

Shred: Reduce Magic Resist

skill.name: Buffer Overflow
skill.desc: Impale 6 feathers into the current target that each deal physical damage. When the target dies, the feathers seek out nearby enemies within 2-hexes, each dealing physical damage.

skill.name: Yuum.AI
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain Mana every second.

Active: Launch a magic missile at the current target that bounces to the nearest enemy. Deal magic damage to the current target and to the other, marking both of them. If they're already marked, deal 190% damage.

skill.name: Replicating Malware
skill.desc:
Passive: At 10% Health, split into two copies with 50% Health.

Active: Bounce 3 times on nearby enemies. Each bounce deals magic damage, Stuns for 1 second, and heals Zac Health.

skill.name: Cutthroat Business
skill.desc: Throw a shuriken at the furthest unmarked enemy within 4 hexes that deals magic damage and marks them. Then become untargetable, teleport to them, and summon shadows on every other marked enemy. Deal physical damage to adjacent enemies, while shadows deal physical damage to adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Hyperthread Rush
skill.desc:
Dash to a nearby location so quickly an untargetable echo lingers. The echo Attacks as if it were Zeri, but deals 40% damage.

Echoes last 5 seconds, and disappear when Zeri dies.

skill.name: Bomberyordle
skill.desc: Throw a bomb that hits the most enemies in a + shape within Attack Range, dealing magic damage. If only one unit is hit, deal 100% more.

skill.name: Stroke of Brilliance
skill.desc: Send a large vine towards the current target, Stunning them for 1 second and dealing magic damage. Send a smaller vine at the nearest target that deals magic damage. Gain all allies 1% Attack Speed.

skill.name: Sentinel Smash
skill.desc: Slam the target dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Training Dummy
skill.desc: Use on a champion to spawn a movable target dummy nearby. Cannot be used in combat.

skill.name: Voidborn
skill.desc: The Voidspawn gains bonus Health and Attack Damage based on the current Stage.
